[01:28.17]the plentiful supply of food thrown overboard by the crews on the rigs;|钻井平台上工作人员扔到海里的大量食物；
[01:34.73]the total absence of fishing boats around the oil rigs.|油井周围完全没有渔船。
[01:39.95]As a result, the fish just eat and eat and grow and grow in the lovely warm water.|因此，鱼儿在温暖的海水中不停地进食、生长。
